quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,1,A sura We have sent down and imposed. We have sent down Clear Signs in it so that hopefully you will pay heed
  24,2,"A woman and a man who commit fornication: flog both of them with one hundred lashes and do not let compassion for either of them possess you where Allah´s deen is concerned, if you have iman in Allah and the Last Day. A number of muminun should witness their punishment"
  24,3,A man who has fornicated may only marry a woman who has fornicated or a woman of the idolaters. A woman who has fornicated may only marry a man who has fornicated or a man of the idolaters. Doing such a thing is haram for the muminun
  24,4,"But those who make accusations against chaste women and then do not produce four witnesses: flog them with eighty lashes and never again accept them as witnesses. Such people are deviators —"
  24,5,"except for those who after that make tawba and put things right. Allah is Ever-Forgiving, Most Merciful"
  24,6,"Those who make an accusation against their wives and have no witnesses except themselves, such people should testify four times by Allah that they are telling the truth"
  24,7,and a fifth time that Allah´s curse will be upon them if they are lying
  24,8,And the punishment is removed from her if she testifies four times by Allah that he is lying
  24,9,and a fifth time that Allah´s anger will be upon her if he is telling the truth
  24,10,"Were it not for Allah´s favour to you and His mercy ...and that Allah is Ever-Returning, All-Wise"